--apla pipes gia epikoinwnia manager-inotifywait
--named pipes gia epikoinwnia manager-worker

--sigaction gia signal handling epeidi einai kalitero apo to signal
--sigint agnoeitai apo olous plin tou manager pou analamvanei na tous skotwsei
--sigchld agnoeitai alla xtin ousia xrhsimopoieitai apo tin entoli
	waitpid(-1,NULL,WNOHANG|WUNTRACED) gia free worker

--o manager an den vrei free worker opws parapanw ftiaxnei allon

--elegkste to path tis inotifywait prin tin ektelesi 
	einai twra /usr/bin/inotifywait
	me which inotifywait vriskw to path sto trexon systima
	


